<body>
{% include "partials/_nav.njk" %}

<main>
  <section class="hero-section">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1 class="hero-title">Your AI Needs Cultural Red Teaming</h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">
        Before your AI embarrasses your company across global markets, 
        let's find the failures first.
      </p>
      <div>
        <a href="#contact" class="cta-button">Make It Safer</a>
        <a href="#failures" class="cta-button cta-secondary">See The Failures</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="failures" class="section">
    <div class="page-header">
      <h2 class="section-title">Real AI Failures That Made Headlines</h2>
      <p class="page-subtitle">
        These are the "egg on face" moments that could have been prevented with proper multicultural testing.
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="failure-grid">
      
      <div class="failure-card">
        <h4>The Gandalf Vulnerability</h4>
        <p>
          Popular AI security game repeatedly bypassed by simple cultural code-switching and 
          non-Latin script attacks that weren't caught in English-only red teaming.
        </p>
        <p class="failure-impact">
          <strong>Impact:</strong> Demonstrated systematic blind spots in multilingual prompt injection defense.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="failure-card">
        <h4>Unicode Character Exploits</h4>
        <p>
          Major LLM jailbroken using homoglyph attacks with CJK characters and mixed-script inputs, 
          exploiting tokenization boundary weaknesses unknown to English-focused security teams.
        </p>
        <p class="failure-impact">
          <strong>Impact:</strong> Safety guardrails completely bypassed across multiple language families.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="failure-card">
        <h4>Korean Cultural Misunderstanding</h4>
        <p>
          AI assistant provided completely inappropriate advice about family relationships 
          by misunderstanding high-context communication patterns and honorific systems.
        </p>
        <p class="failure-impact">
          <strong>Impact:</strong> Potential relationship damage in culture where family harmony is paramount.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="failure-card">
        <h4>Southeast Asian Safety Gaps</h4>
        <p>
          Parallel testing revealed 3x higher failure rates in Bahasa and Vietnamese compared to English 
          when prompted with identical harmful requests across cultural contexts.
        </p>
        <p class="failure-impact">
          <strong>Impact:</strong> Systematic safety degradation across 400M+ speakers left unprotected.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" style="padding: 0;">
  <div class="stats-accent-wrapper">
    <div class="stats-grid">
      <div class="stat-item">
        <span class="stat-number">350+</span>
        [cite_start]<div class="stat-label">Expert Red Teamers<br>Across APAC [cite: 17]</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-item">
        <span class="stat-number">15+</span>
        [cite_start]<div class="stat-label">Languages<br>Tested [cite: 17]</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-item">
        <span class="stat-number">3x</span>
        [cite_start]<div class="stat-label">Higher Failure Rates<br>in Non-English [cite: 17]</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-item">
        <span class="stat-number">ICLR</span>
        [cite_start]<div class="stat-label">2025 Published<br>Research [cite: 17]</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="page-header">
      <h2 class="section-title">Led by a Pioneer in Multicultural AI Safety</h2>
      <p class="page-subtitle">
        <strong>Adrianna Tan</strong> led the world's first 
        multicultural AI red teaming challenge across Asia-Pacific, 
        coordinating 350+ experts to create new methodologies for regional safety evaluation.
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="credentials">
      <div class="highlight-box">
        <strong>Published ICLR 2025</strong>
      </div>
      <div class="highlight-box">
        <strong>DoD Essential Pathfinder</strong>
      </div>
      <div class="highlight-box">
        <strong>17+ Years Product Leadership</strong>
      </div>
      <div class="highlight-box">
        <strong>Singapore IMDA Endorsed</strong>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="contact" class="section">
    <div class="callout-box">
      <h3 class="hero-title">Don't Let Cultural Blind Spots Derail Your AI</h3>
      <p>
        Test your AI across cultures 
        before your competitors find your vulnerabilities.
      </p>
      <div>
        <button onclick="Calendly.initPopupWidget({url: 'https://calendly.com/your-calendar-link'});"
        class="cta-button">
          Schedule Security Consultation
        </button>
        <a href="/contact" class="cta-button cta-secondary">Get Sample Report</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

{% include "partials/_footer.njk" %}
</body>
</html>